videos.headline: Gus Ragland to Kenny Young puts Miami, OH on the board
videos.description: Gus Ragland hits Kenny Young from 5 yards out to give Miami, OH the early lead.

videos.headline: JaVaughn Craig fools the Miami, OH defense for TD
videos.description: JaVaughn Craig's 22-yard touchdown run ties the game for Austin Peay.

videos.headline: Gus Ragland finds James Gardner for TD and lead
videos.description: Gus Ragland hits James Gardner from 42 yards away to reclaim the lead for Miami, OH.

videos.headline: Leonard Ross bulls into the endzone to widen Miami, (OH) lead
videos.description: Leonard Ross scores from one-yard out to pad the lead.

videos.headline: Miami, (OH) dominates Austin Peay
videos.description: Jeff McCorrogher and Bobby Carpenter break down Miami, (OH) 31-10 victory over Austin Peay.
